---
layout: layout.njk
title: Best AI Tools for UK Trades
permalink: /best-ai-tools-uk/
---
<section class="space-y-4">
  <p class="section-kicker">Business Types</p>
  <h1 class="page-title">Best AI Tools for UK Businesses</h1>
  <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-700">
    Choose a business type to browse curated tool guides. Trade-specific pathways are live now,
    with additional business types planned.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
  <a class="panel p-5 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md" href="{{ '/best-ai-tools-uk/trades/' | url }}">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Trades</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
      Browse electrician and other trade-specific tool reviews.
    </p>
  </a>
  <article class="panel p-5">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">More Business Types</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
      Planned next: additional sectors using the same content model and URL system.
    </p>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
  <h2 class="col-span-full text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Current Trade Categories</h2>
  {% for cat in collections.businessCategories %}
    <a class="panel p-5 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md" href="{{ cat.tag | tagHref | url }}">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">{{ cat.label }}</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
        {{ cat.count }} guide{% if cat.count != 1 %}s{% endif %} focused on UK {{ cat.label | lower }} businesses.
      </p>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</section>
